name: Integrity DAO
description: $ID, the Integrity DAO token, is the governance token of Avalanche's (and Wall Street Bets') legendary Integrity DAO - a collective of leading Avalanche builders, influencers, investors, and supporters - and now anyone can participate in the DAO by holding and voting the token! Our DAO treasury already holds over $1 million in assets under management, and everything we own and do is allocated solely to the advancement of the Avalanche ecosystem!
